for 800 g cooked rice
rinse rice before cooking 

meat
 - 150 g cooked silked chicken

whisk together
 - 4 eggs
 - 1 pinch salt
 - 1 pinch msg

armomatics
 - 4-8 garlic cloves
 - 2 minced shallots
 - 2 tbsp minced ginger

prepare and keep seperate
 - 1/4 cup small diced carrots 
 - 1/4 cup peas
 - 6 green onions white part

sauce
 - 3 tbsp soy sauce
 - 2 tbsp oyster sauce
 - 1 tsp sugar

spices
 - 1 tsp msg
 - 1 tsp salt
 - 1/2 tsp white pepper

garnish
 - 6 green onions green part
 - 2 tsp sesame oil

lightly coat a pan with oil
heat until starting to smoke
turn heat to medium 
add
 - 2 tbsp oil
add carrots 
cook 1 minute
add aromatics 
cook 1 minute
turn heat to high
add rice
cook 3 minutes
push rice in the middle
add sauce around rice
add white part of green onions
add peas 
cook 2 minutes
stir in dry spices
cook 1 minute until dry 
push rice in the middle
